description:
Join us for Season three as we continue our Lineage Journey from the very beginning of time. Travel with us around the globe as we look at how God led his people through captivity and conquest. We continue to trace our spiritual roots back to the origins and see that even in the face of sorrow and death there is always hope.

#KnowYourHistory #KnowYourMission #KnowYourOrigins #Lineage #LineageJourney 

www.lineagejourney.com
